# Deploy on every change

When the user asks for a code or design change on this project:

1. Make the requested changes
2. Commit to git (clear message focused on why)
3. Push to `origin` (`main`)
4. Deploy to Vercel production with `vercel --prod --yes`

Do this without waiting to be asked to deploy, unless the user explicitly says not to deploy.
Production alias: https://www.truckersoftheworld.com
